article.description: — Tylan Pope recorded 12 points and 10 rebounds to lift Tulane to a 66-57 win over Lamar on Friday.
article.headline: Pope lifts Tulane over Lamar 66-57
article.story: NEW ORLEANS -- — Tylan Pope recorded 12 points and 10 rebounds to lift Tulane to a 66-57 win over Lamar on Friday. Jaylen Forbes had 15 points and seven rebounds for Tulane (1-0). Sion James added six rebounds. Anderson Kopp had 18 points and seven rebounds for the Cardinals (0-2). Quinlan Bennett added 14 points and Ellis Jefferson had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
